---
title: Asian-Style Glazed Beef Rump & Sesame Fries with Kohlrabi Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Tonight’s dinner takes steak and veg to new levels. As if beef rump glazed in honey and soy sauce wasn’t delicious enough, serving it alongside sesame fries and a Japanese slaw adds another flavour punch! A dollop of garlic aioli adds the perfect amount of creaminess to this irresistible dish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
